title: The Return of the Regulator
text:
The Return of the Regulator is the fourth studio album by <a href="Warren%20G">Warren G</a>. The album can be considered a return to <a href="G-funk">the roots</a> of <a href="West%20Coast%20hip%20hop">west coast</a> <a href="gangsta%20rap">gangsta music</a>, but it sold less than the rapper's two previous albums.
Samples.
Ghetto Village
